{"tid":36073,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"新田公廁新照太驚豔！日宅盛贊新田公廁瘦成大美人","createTime":"2016-12-12T12:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T02:05:57.000Z","uid":30256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f6f38f8e11379c2ed39d6927d5dc7ef2ffe3631","tid":36073,"uid":30256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"《LoveLive！》中&mu;\\'s的隊長聲優新田公廁從進入今年下半年以來，每次露面都被日宅盛贊瘦成美人，在12月10日剛剛度過了生日的新田公廁在推特上放出了自己過生日時的照片，再次引發日宅盛贊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/57t1w2ze\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F57t1w2ze&h=1c3b0a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新田公廁在推文中答謝了參加她的生日派對的各位，並表示自己非常幸福，同時她還配上了一張比出V字手，笑得很開心的照片。照片中的新田露出了甜美的笑容，臉上畫著淡雅清新的妝，顯得非常清爽幹淨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jlif59rv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjlif59rv&h=7f6a2608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這張照片很快引起了日宅的盛贊，日宅們紛紛評論道：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;公廁在真的瘦成大美人了，去年她上紅白簡直肥成直播事故了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;公廁在最近越來越美了，果然是最棒的隊長！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;感覺自從AV門之後她就開始減肥了，而且越來越美，這是對黑子的反擊嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.myfreeanime.com/ca-51/ar-75279.html?utm_source=ACGFANS&amp;utm_medium=page&amp;utm_campaign=ACGFANS&amp;utm_term=196501167039848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.myfreeanime.com%2Fca-51%2Far-75279.html%3Futm_source%3DACGFANS%26utm_medium%3Dpage%26utm_campaign%3DACGFANS%26utm_term%3D196501167039848&d=AbwkItc77YSrWZPGCDlQwmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=773d8605\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.myfreeanime.com/ca-51/ar-75279.html?utm_source=ACGFANS&amp;utm_medium=page&amp;utm_campaign=ACGFANS&amp;utm_term=196501167039848</a>"},{"pid":"87a8b6ca89e4bcf91ff100a43afdd07d5dd1e253","tid":36073,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"終於唔係肥海"},{"pid":"1541a0d1373f01832e8b246c1611fda7a95d92f7","tid":36073,"uid":62343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0